title: ‘Ukuhumusha’—A New Way to Hack OpenAI's ChatGPT
description: Researchers have discovered OpenAI's GPT-4’s security settings are ill-equipped to handle languages not commonly fed into its training data.

title: Charles Hoskinson Fires Back at Critics, Defends Cardano Ecosystem
description:

On an X (formerly Twitter) post, Hoskinson replied to a user by the name of Swan.ada, who shared negative opinions about Cardano and Hoskinson in particular.
